          "stats": {
            "description": {
              "value": "Your exposure to the Shadowfell's magic grants you the following benefits.\n\nAbility Score Increase. Increase your Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma by 1, to a maximum of 20.\n\nShadow Magic. Choose one level 1 spell from the Illusion or Necromancy school of magic. You always have that spell and the Invisibility spell prepared. You can cast each of these spells without expending a spell slot. Once you cast either spell in this way, you can't cast that spell in this way again until you finish a Long Rest. You can also cast these spells using spell slots you have of the appropriate level. The spells' spellcasting ability is the ability increased by this feat"
            },
